!! MIIT Beian Number

;Your MIIT ICP/Service Record Number: (for example, `沪ICP备12345678号-1` or `津公网安备12345678901234号`)
:<$edit-text tiddler="$:/plugins/linonetwo/beian-miit/configs/MIITBeianNumber" tabindex=-1 focus=false cancelPopups="yes" fileDrop=no tag="input" placeholder="填写您的备案号" />

''Note:'' When you fill in the beian number, it will be displayed at the bottom of the page with a link to https://beian.miit.gov.cn. Leave it empty to hide the beian footer.
